        <abstract> 
<p>A letter from Asa Gray informs CD that Ticknor &amp; Fields will not publish a new edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> to compete with Appleton’s unrevised edition. They recommend sending copies of the English edition for the American market.</p> 
